data.description: Welcome to 276 Jadetree Drive. This home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and 1201 square feet. As you walk in you are welcomed by the open living room area with tall ceilings and LVP flooring. Heading into the kitchen you will find granite counter tops, newer appliances, and tile flooring. You will have a great eat in kitchen area that offers enough space for at least a 6 top table. Down the hall you will have your spacious owner’s suite bedroom with a private bath, accompanied by the secondary bedroom and the shared bath. On the other side of the home, you will find your 3rd bedroom with tile flooring and great views of the front of the home. This home has a lot to offer, call us to schedule your private showing today!
